Next, watch what we learned from

214
00:08:43,800 --> 00:08:46,080
analyzing a thousand onboarding flows

215
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:48,320
and what separates intuitive dashboards

216
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:51,040
from overwhelming ones across 2,000

